{
  "stem": "9601.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So you see, I'm talking about the Teslers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "All these are interrelated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They had a little sister, called Datia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She perished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You see, Eva, Chava, the first daughter, she was a widow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she married-- she remarried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She married Shabtai, because Sheyndel, the first wife of Shabtai, died giving birth to Datia-- Datia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So later on, the two got together, you know, a widower and a widow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So they already in the family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He married Eva.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He perished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He and Pinchas were walking from one village to another.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they were caught in a gully.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And Pinchas was shot in the leg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But he was younger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He got out of the gully and survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But Shabtai, his father, was wounded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they threw him into a well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Bad.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then, there was Malka and Chana, two sisters on my mother's.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They were one-- Malka Uster and her son, and her husband, came into our village, because they couldn't stay in Klevan, because over there, is a city.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And right away, the ghettos [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "So they stayed in our village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And Chana lived in Rowne, but her husband, Moses [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Melamud-- ?] Moses, was in the Polish army before the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "So when the war broke out, he stayed in the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Never came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Either he died on the front lines-- whichever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "He never showed up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "But they-- she-- they had a son, Rachmiel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And now he's [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Emmuel. ?] He lives in New York.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "His mother remarried, so he's actually [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Emmuel ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Marder. ?] He went to his-- took his step-father's name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "But I don't think he ever knew his father, because he was just a little baby.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "They came to live in our village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And they survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "But Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
